name: CWNetworkProfile
desc: Encapsulates an immutable network profile entry.

items.name: init()
items.desc: Creates and returns a CWNetworkProfile object.

items.name: init(networkProfile: CWNetworkProfile)
items.desc: Creates and returns a CWNetworkProfile object initialized with the given CWNetworkProfile object.

items.name: var security: CWSecurity
items.desc: The security mode for the network profile.

items.name: var ssid: String?
items.desc: The service set identifier (SSID) for the network profile, encoded as a string.

items.name: var ssidData: Data?
items.desc: The service set identifier (SSID) for the network profile, returned as data.
